      <title>美联储将华尔街降息愿望摆上台面 股市飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stocks-soar-as-fed-puts-wall-street-s-rate-cut-wish-on-the-table</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔为在 9 月的下次央行会议上降低借贷成本留下了空间，交易员对即将降息的前景持乐观态度，周三，买入信号闪现在华尔街各处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stocks-soar-as-fed-puts-wall-street-s-rate-cut-wish-on-the-table</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:25:36 GMT</pubDate>
